    "It is determined by computing the mean of the AP values for each category, as formulated in Equation (3).𝑚𝐴𝑃 = ∑ 𝐴𝑣𝑒𝑃(𝑞) 𝑄 𝑞=1 𝑄(3)The primary evaluation metric for this study employs the same assessment method used in the COCO dataset, adopting the most commonly used evaluation metric in the field of object detection, mAP.",
    "D. Experimental DesignIn terms of feature extraction, given the critical role of feature extraction algorithms in subsequent object detection algorithms, this study parallelly constructed Faster RCNN networks based on ResNet50, ResNet101, and ResNeSt50 as the basic feature extraction networks, comparing the model accuracy of different feature extraction networks.",
    "The efficacy of an object detection algorithm is intrinsically linked to the prowess of its feature extraction network, which is pivotal to the final detection accuracy of the model.",
